= Dragon Warrior IV (NES) Monster List =

This page documents all monsters in '''Dragon Warrior IV''' (NES, US version).

== Overview ==

Dragon Warrior IV contains approximately 180 unique monster entries, though some slots are unused or duplicates. Monsters are stored in Bank $06 starting at address $A2A2, with 27 bytes per entry.

== Monster Data Structure ==

Each monster uses 27 bytes:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $00-$14 || 21 || Graphics/Animation data
|-
| $15-$16 || 2 || HP (big-endian)
|-
| $17 || 1 || Attack
|-
| $18 || 1 || Defense
|-
| $19 || 1 || Agility
|-
| $1A || 1 || Behavior flags
|-
| $1B-$1C || 2 || Experience (big-endian)
|-
| $1D-$1E || 2 || Gold (big-endian)
|-
| $1F || 1 || Drop rate
|-
| $20 || 1 || Drop item ID
|-
| $21 || 1 || Status immunities
|}

