== Monster Behavior Flags ==

Byte at offset $1A controls AI behavior:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Bit !! Meaning
|-
| 0 || Can use healing magic
|-
| 1 || Can use attack magic
|-
| 2 || Can use support magic
|-
| 3 || Can call for help
|-
| 4 || Prioritizes fleeing
|-
| 5 || Immune to flee
|-
| 6 || Boss flag
|-
| 7 || Metal flag (high DEF, EXP)
|}

